# Prettier also skips everything in .gitignore (node_modules/, dashboard/data/, plans/, logs/, …).
# Markdown (README, CLAUDE.md, prompts/) is hand-formatted — line breaks there are deliberate.
*.md
# The two dashboard pages are hand-written zero-build HTML; Prettier's HTML style reflows them
# wholesale (attribute-per-line, void slashes) for no correctness gain — they stay hand-formatted.
# (JS is still formatted — with embeddedLanguageFormatting off, so the html`` markup the renderers
# build from deliberately-unbalanced tag fragments is never "corrected" by the HTML formatter.)
*.html
